# Getting Started
---

Since the bulk of our time will be spent on javascript, **specifically** javascript logic, we will use a **[tool](http://samantha.fewd.us/)**

<pre class='js-executable' style="display: none;">
Array.from(
document.querySelectorAll('.js-content a')
).forEach(function(item) {
item.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
const href = e.target.getAttribute('href');
if ( href.split('#').length > 2 ) {
e.preventDefault();
window.open(href);
}
});
});
</pre>
